title: Hanefi Mahçiçek
text: Hanefi Mahçiçek was a <a href="Turkish%20people">Turkish</a> <a href="politician">politician</a> and <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="chairman">chairman</a>. He was born in <a href="Kahramanmara%C5%9F">Kahramanmaraş</a>. He was the chairman of <a href="Kahramanmara%C5%9Fspor">Kahramanmaraşspor</a>.
